22
00:02:31,600 --> 00:02:34,880
There. Drink up!

23
00:02:36,280 --> 00:02:37,450
Here.

24
00:02:37,450 --> 00:02:39,170
You should have plenty as well.

25
00:02:39,170 --> 00:02:41,320
The king should drink up first.

26
00:02:41,320 --> 00:02:43,800
The queen should drink up first.

27
00:02:43,800 --> 00:02:46,180
<i>He's changed his tactics.</i>

28
00:02:46,180 --> 00:02:49,940
<i> I know all your dark thoughts well.</i>

29
00:02:51,040 --> 00:02:53,660
Then let's each have a drink in good favor

30
00:02:53,660 --> 00:02:56,610
