31
00:02:56,610 --> 00:02:59,640
Like hell. We were just getting started!

32
00:02:59,640 --> 00:03:04,580
Let's not do that and take this lovely one-shot like a man!

33
00:03:04,580 --> 00:03:06,730
One sho—

34
00:03:08,700 --> 00:03:12,300
I have sensitive sleeping habits, so make sure to keep your distance.

35
00:03:12,300 --> 00:03:15,580
<i>What kind of crappy tactic is that?</i>

36
00:03:26,460 --> 00:03:30,340
<i>[Wins in the morning and withdraws at night.]</i>

37
00:03:32,690 --> 00:03:35,180
Oh, I see...

38
00:03:35,180 --> 00:03:38,540
<i>The king who was known for his love of alcohol and women...</i>

39
00:03:43,230 --> 00:03:45,000
<i>I was scared for no reason!</i>

40
00:03:45,000 --> 00:03:48,460
<i>Still, I can't let my guard down.</i>

41
00:03:51,980 --> 00:03:56,400
<i>I'm finally using the granny knot I learned during my military service.</i>

42
00:03:56,400 --> 00:03:59,340
<i>He'll have to cut it to get this off.</i>

43
00:03:59,340 --> 00:04:01,190
Okay.

44
00:04:05,340 --> 00:04:10,430
<i>This selfish king bastard. He's hogging the comfortable blankets to himself.</i>

45
00:04:21,190 --> 00:04:25,020
Queen, it is not that I do not understand how you feel;

46
00:04:25,020 --> 00:04:27,400
