47
00:04:27,400 --> 00:04:32,110
It's not that. I was brought up very delicately, so I can't sleep on the bare floor.

48
00:04:32,110 --> 00:04:34,230
Just give me one.

49
00:04:34,230 --> 00:04:38,950
If even one layer is missing from a 3-layer bed, I can't sleep.

50
00:04:40,130 --> 00:04:43,030
I doubt you were brought up more delicately than the king.

51
00:04:47,100 --> 00:04:50,560
<i>It's a historical distortion. He's nothing but a young master of Ganghwa.</i>

52
00:05:12,590 --> 00:05:14,890
<i>I hope he gets sleep paralysis.</i>

53
00:05:18,940 --> 00:05:23,020
<i>Since things ended up this way, I'll take the first watch.</i>

54
00:05:23,940 --> 00:05:27,630
I keep getting reminded of my enlistment days.

55
00:05:40,740 --> 00:05:44,290
<i>[Episode 2]
[Nobody Knows]</i>

56
00:06:42,210 --> 00:06:44,350
<i>Have you awoken, Your Majesty?</i>

57
00:06:44,350 --> 00:06:46,730
Damn it.

58
00:06:46,730 --> 00:06:49,850
I had my doubts, but sure enough, I'm still here.

59
00:06:51,420 --> 00:06:55,570
How does it feel after your first night as Your Majesty the Queen?

60
00:06:55,570 --> 00:06:57,610
Like f**k.

61
00:06:58,860 --> 00:07:00,650
Dear me.

62
00:07:02,140 --> 00:07:04,970
Huh? My granny knot.

63
00:07:08,730 --> 00:07:11,060
Did you lose something again?

64
00:07:11,060 --> 00:07:14,800
- This time, I will look thoroughly—
- No!

65
00:07:14,800 --> 00:07:19,570
<i>I probably undid it in my sleep because I was uncomfortable, right?</i>

66
00:07:19,570 --> 00:07:22,930
No!

67
00:07:59,740 --> 00:08:01,510
Your Majesty!

68
00:08:06,200 --> 00:08:08,900
Why have you awoken so early, Your Majesty?

69
00:08:08,900 --> 00:08:12,100
I deeply apologize for not escorting you.

70
00:08:12,100 --> 00:08:16,560
I did not want to disturb the queen's sleep, so I slipped out quietly.

71
00:08:16,560 --> 00:08:20,020
Did you have another nightmare?

72
00:08:21,350 --> 00:08:26,500
The queen cannot be disturbed from sleep because of me. It is her first day as queen, after all.

73
00:08:26,500 --> 00:08:31,570
I will prepare jasmine tea again for a restful sleep tonight.

74
00:08:33,760 --> 00:08:38,520
The queen is probably on her way to greet the elders, correct?

75
00:08:38,520 --> 00:08:41,670
I heard she has just departed.

76
00:08:41,670 --> 00:08:45,930
I am looking forward to seeing how she will act.

77
00:08:50,740 --> 00:08:53,200
There was a wedding yesterday, so fine.

78
00:08:53,200 --> 00:08:55,690
But why am I busy from the second I wake up again today?

79
00:08:55,690 --> 00:09:00,210
Now is when you formally greet Grand Queen Dowager and Queen Dowager.

80
00:09:00,210 --> 00:09:03,390
You must also be greeted by government officials.

81
00:09:03,390 --> 00:09:05,710
Once the official celebration is done—

82
00:09:05,710 --> 00:09:07,610
That's when the royal wedding is over?

83
00:09:07,610 --> 00:09:12,960
No, His Majesty the King has to issue a message announcing the investiture of the queen.

84
00:09:14,240 --> 00:09:17,780
It's a never-ending wedding.

85
00:09:17,780 --> 00:09:20,980
Hold on. If it's Grand Queen Dowager...

86
00:09:20,980 --> 00:09:24,150
<i>This is what Grand Queen Dowager herself ordered</i>

87
00:09:24,150 --> 00:09:28,520
<i>If I were to refill the lake, I would be going against her wishes.</i>

88
00:09:32,050 --> 00:09:34,430
What is Grand Queen Dowager like?

89
00:09:34,430 --> 00:09:39,190
Grand Queen Dowager is the elder from the same Andong Kim family as Your Majesty,

90
00:09:39,190 --> 00:09:43,160
and Queen Dowager is from the Pungyang Jo family.

91
00:09:44,090 --> 00:09:46,970
My mother-in-law and grandmother-in-law are rivals.

92
00:09:46,970 --> 00:09:49,760
I, the queen, am on my grandmother-in-law's side.

93
00:09:49,760 --> 00:09:51,910
<i>I should be able to tell which is which, right?</i>

94
00:09:51,910 --> 00:09:55,100
<i>Since the older one will be Grand Queen Dowager.</i>

95
00:09:55,100 --> 00:09:56,850
What else?

96
00:09:57,930 --> 00:10:02,350
This is very important to me, so tell me everything you know.

97
00:10:02,350 --> 00:10:04,700
She is the older sister of Lord Kim Jwa-geun.

98
00:10:04,700 --> 00:10:08,570
Upon entering the palace, she has never once set foot outside the palace.

99
00:10:08,570 --> 00:10:10,770
- Furthermore—
- Stop.

100
00:10:12,970 --> 00:10:14,760
Not you, the palanquin!

101
00:10:14,760 --> 00:10:17,360
Stop! (English was not used in the Joseon era) Stop!

102
00:10:17,360 --> 00:10:19,850
Halt!

103
00:10:23,490 --> 00:10:28,130
Back, back, back! (English) Reverse, reverse, reverse!

104
00:10:28,130 --> 00:10:30,520
Reverse!

105
00:10:35,340 --> 00:10:36,950
Stop!

106
00:10:43,820 --> 00:10:47,070
I just found something more important to do.

107
00:11:19,260 --> 00:11:23,860
Did you lose your way because of the palace's complex layout?

108
00:11:27,730 --> 00:11:31,330
It's a pleasure to meet you. And you are?

109
00:11:35,390 --> 00:11:36,750
Seriously.

110
00:11:36,750 --> 00:11:40,490
I'm still not yet used to this body.

111
00:11:43,320 --> 00:11:47,290
Your elegant bearing is not ordinary at all.

112
00:11:47,290 --> 00:11:48,790
Are you a member of the royal family, too?

113
00:11:48,790 --> 00:11:53,420
Perhaps, are you a princess or something?

114
00:11:53,420 --> 00:11:54,970
I apologize.

115
00:11:54,970 --> 00:12:00,000
If I have offended you with my arrogance, please forgive me, Your Majesty.

116
00:12:00,000 --> 00:12:03,720
- No, no. What I was trying to say was that—
- Your Majesty!

117
00:12:03,720 --> 00:12:07,790
You walk so quickly that you've already come this far.

118
00:12:07,790 --> 00:12:09,840
Greetings, My Lady.

119
00:12:11,200 --> 00:12:12,950
Do you know her?

120
00:12:14,030 --> 00:12:18,780
She is Lady Hwa-jin, the daughter of Lord Jo. She is to become the king's royal concubine.

121
00:12:19,900 --> 00:12:23,160
I know she's the queen, but she's messing with you too much!

122
00:12:23,160 --> 00:12:24,590
She keeps being sarcastic!

123
00:12:24,590 --> 00:12:28,390
There's a rumor in the palace that she was the one who pushed Your Majesty into the lake.

124
00:12:28,390 --> 00:12:32,180
I'm certain that the rumors that the queen lost her memory are lies.

125
00:12:32,180 --> 00:12:34,680
- You should be careful.
- You should be careful.

126
00:12:42,380 --> 00:12:49,170
I'm pretty good with physiognomy since I've spent a lot of time with women. <i>(Assessing one's character from facial features)</i>

127
00:12:49,170 --> 00:12:54,930
How should I put this? You are a good person.

128
00:12:57,960 --> 00:13:03,000
I guess you and this person haven't had the best relationship in the past, but shall we start anew?

129
00:13:03,000 --> 00:13:05,270
I like you.

130
00:13:06,640 --> 00:13:08,580
Let's be friends.

131
00:13:12,420 --> 00:13:15,600
Did you decide to change your method?

132
00:13:15,600 --> 00:13:17,660
Method?

133
00:13:17,660 --> 00:13:21,280
Thanks to you, I have a very clear picture of what this place is like.

134
00:13:21,280 --> 00:13:23,470
Now I feel like I'm in the palace.

135
00:13:23,470 --> 00:13:27,730
No, no. I think you misunderstood me a little bit.

136
00:13:27,730 --> 00:13:30,560
I apologize, but I must go.

137
00:13:32,780 --> 00:13:35,360
Your Majesty.

138
00:13:35,360 --> 00:13:37,100
- Your Majesty.
- Your Majesty.

139
00:13:37,100 --> 00:13:40,050
I went to the royal villa, but you were not there.

140
00:13:40,050 --> 00:13:43,090
I also went to give you my greetings, but you were not there.

141
00:13:43,090 --> 00:13:48,770
We must have missed each other. Our hearts connected.

142
00:13:50,590 --> 00:13:54,550
<i>If she's the royal concubine, then she's Cheoljong's second wife?</i>

143
00:13:54,550 --> 00:13:58,640
<i>I should have entered that body, not this one! </i>

144
00:13:59,600 --> 00:14:03,820
The jealousy in Her Majesty's eyes makes me tremble with fear.

145
00:14:08,600 --> 00:14:11,590
All right, get a room.

146
00:14:11,590 --> 00:14:17,150
My Queen, I'd like you to hurry up the investiture of the royal concubine.

147
00:14:20,020 --> 00:14:24,490
What to do? I can't do that because I'm too busy.

148
00:14:24,490 --> 00:14:26,310
It's a royal command.

149
00:14:27,840 --> 00:14:30,740
<i>Screw you, polygamist!</i>

150
00:14:32,260 --> 00:14:37,650
Your Majesty, the elders of the Inner Court are waiting for you—

151
00:14:37,650 --> 00:14:39,450
Your Majesty!

152
00:14:41,500 --> 00:14:44,400
Well, I have something important to do.

153
00:14:50,990 --> 00:14:53,120
What was that!

154
00:14:59,140 --> 00:15:01,810
You must have been startled.

155
00:15:03,350 --> 00:15:09,120
Hwa-jin, I'll finally be able to have you as my wife.

156
00:15:09,120 --> 00:15:13,030
Now, I live in the same palace as you.

157
00:15:13,030 --> 00:15:16,600
We have to go through the customary formalities. Actually,

158
00:15:16,600 --> 00:15:20,080
the head sulli saw you at the lake.
<i>(Sulli - eunuch in charge of gifts and food for the king)</i>

159
00:15:20,080 --> 00:15:25,890
They were trying to blame you for the lake incident, so I had to rush the installation.

160
00:15:25,890 --> 00:15:30,100
I was just surprised to hear a loud noise from the lake...

161
00:15:30,100 --> 00:15:31,790
Don't worry.

162
00:15:31,790 --> 00:15:36,120
Even the Andong Kim family cannot do anything to you when you are innocent.

163
00:15:42,670 --> 00:15:46,170
No, I will make it so that they can't do anything to you.

164
00:15:46,170 --> 00:15:49,400
I will put everything on the line and protect you.

165
00:15:50,510 --> 00:15:52,770
Your Majesty.

166
00:15:52,770 --> 00:15:56,250
But I surely have nothing to offer you.

167
00:15:56,250 --> 00:16:00,190
Just a mere throne for appearance, a brother who's full of worry,

168
00:16:00,190 --> 00:16:02,290
one troublemaker of a friend,

169
00:16:02,290 --> 00:16:07,430
and... one beautiful woman.

170
00:16:12,930 --> 00:16:15,060
You're rich.

171
00:16:16,490 --> 00:16:22,320
Your whereabouts on that day have been fully accounted for, so don't worry.

172
00:16:35,630 --> 00:16:37,890
<i>What? Who is Grand Queen Dowager?</i>

173
00:16:37,890 --> 00:16:40,850
Please give your greetings, Your Majesty.

174
00:16:40,850 --> 00:16:43,090
<i>Damn it! Whatever!</i>

175
00:16:43,090 --> 00:16:48,300
I hope you had a peaceful night, Your Royal Highness, Grand Queen Dowager.

176
00:16:55,620 --> 00:17:00,360
The night has rejuvenated you so well that you’ve regained your youth!

177
00:17:00,360 --> 00:17:03,930
I nearly mistook you for Queen Dowager!

178
00:17:03,930 --> 00:17:06,050
This wench!

179
00:17:06,050 --> 00:17:08,200
Is that so?

180
00:17:08,200 --> 00:17:11,340
It was worth all my effort then!

181
00:17:11,340 --> 00:17:13,780
<i>Good. That was natural.</i>

182
00:17:13,780 --> 00:17:16,910
After that tragic accident...

183
00:17:16,910 --> 00:17:21,490
Oh my. It seems to me that you haven’t fully recovered.

184
00:17:21,490 --> 00:17:23,410
Can't you tell at once?

185
00:17:23,410 --> 00:17:26,100
She has the perfect appearance of a queen!

186
00:17:26,100 --> 00:17:28,480
Her keen eye is as good as ever!

187
00:17:28,480 --> 00:17:34,620
Yes. Oh my, yes. You're right.

188
00:17:34,620 --> 00:17:38,290
<i>A war of nerves with a smile on their faces.</i>.

189
00:17:38,290 --> 00:17:40,320
<i>I better keep my head on straight.</i>

190
00:17:40,320 --> 00:17:43,890
Now, you just have to put all your effort into giving us an heir.

191
00:17:43,890 --> 00:17:48,250
Ah, there is a secret to conceiving a prince,

192
00:17:48,250 --> 00:17:51,410
which has been passed down from generation to generation in the palace.

193
00:17:52,900 --> 00:17:55,200
Is that so?

194
00:17:55,200 --> 00:18:02,420
This is what you have to do when you spend the night with the King. When he’s lying down on his back, you can...

195
00:18:18,600 --> 00:18:23,030
<i>She’s the worst mother-in-law I’ve ever seen.</i>

196
00:18:23,030 --> 00:18:26,600
And at the exact moment, you must—

197
00:18:26,600 --> 00:18:30,100
Mother, I’ll take care of that myself!

198
00:18:35,440 --> 00:18:38,260
<i>Oh, I should have held that in! </i>

199
00:18:38,260 --> 00:18:43,130
Well, I am well-educated in those things.

200
00:18:52,170 --> 00:18:57,860
That’s right! You took a lot of bridal classes to become a good wife to him.

201
00:18:57,860 --> 00:19:01,210
I’m sure you’re very well prepared for that.

202
00:19:01,210 --> 00:19:02,900
I see.

203
00:19:02,900 --> 00:19:07,420
I've been overstepping.

204
00:19:09,380 --> 00:19:13,170
<i>She doesn't like having a second-class daughter-in-law,</i>

205
00:19:13,170 --> 00:19:17,250
<i>but it's thrilling when the daughter-in-law's daughter-in-law is second-class.</i>

206
00:19:24,370 --> 00:19:27,370
<i>[Injeong-jeon]</i>
<i>(The throne room)</i>

207
00:19:33,610 --> 00:19:36,870
Ah, so cumbersome! There sure are many ways to kill a person, really!

208
00:19:36,870 --> 00:19:39,180
Ah, my neck hurts!

209
00:19:39,180 --> 00:19:41,360
You look very tired.

210
00:19:41,360 --> 00:19:45,550
I suppose we did overdo it last night.

211
00:19:45,550 --> 00:19:48,040
We didn't even drink that much.

212
00:19:48,040 --> 00:19:52,200
They are waiting for us. Please enter.

213
