Congratulations.

220
00:21:00,620 --> 00:21:03,160
<i>One after another, family name: Kim.</i>

221
00:21:03,160 --> 00:21:07,070
<i>So they are the famous Andong Kims?</i>

222
00:21:08,440 --> 00:21:12,210
<i>With Grand Royal Queen Dowager and the king's consort on their side,</i>

