Right State Councilor, Jo Man-hong.

229
00:21:36,650 --> 00:21:39,720
Congratulations.

230
00:21:39,720 --> 00:21:43,680
Minister of Personnel, Jo Deok-moon.

231
00:21:43,680 --> 00:21:45,780
Congratulations.

232
00:21:45,780 --> 00:21:48,240
<i>Ah, the Pungyang Jo family.</i>

233
00:21:48,240 --> 00:21:50,860
<i>This family with Queen Dowager Jo as its head is also famous.</i>

234
