00:43:17,020 --> 00:43:20,420
<i>You must love me!</i>

472
00:43:24,320 --> 00:43:29,580
<i>His gaze was full of hate. It's more than just not loving her, he hates her! </i>

473
00:43:31,110 --> 00:43:33,290
<i>Please, Your Majesty!</i>

474
00:43:38,250 --> 00:43:40,950
<i>I prefer snacks to alcohol.</i>

475
00:43:40,950 --> 00:43:44,700
<i>That's great. All the alcohol in this room is for you my queen.</i>

476
00:43:44,700 --> 00:43:48,250
<i>From the beginning, Cheoljong had no intention of spending the night with her.</i>

477
00:43:48,250 --> 00:43:53,720
<i>That's why he tried to give me a drink. He had the same plan as I did.</i>

478
00:43:53,720 --> 00:43:56,740
<i>Now, all you have to do is give us an heir.</i>

479
00:43:56,740 --> 00:43:59,340
<i>Please recover your senses, Your Majesty!</i>

480
00:43:59,340 --> 00:44:01,150
<i>Bring some water! Water!</i>

481
00:44:01,150 --> 00:44:07,530
<i>Cheoljong did it to fool the Kim clan, who was trying to convince him to sleep with her.</i>

482
00:44:13,330 --> 00:44:16,660
Hong Yeon, nothing happened to me!

483
00:44:18,040 --> 00:44:24,420
I was so bothered! I trusted myself but couldn't trust that bastard. But...

484
00:44:27,470 --> 00:44:29,400
What are you all doing?

485
00:44:46,130 --> 00:44:48,810
More! Pull them up. More!

486
00:44:48,810 --> 00:44:50,760
Yes, Your Highness.

487
00:44:52,330 --> 00:44:55,610
This is how difficult maintaining my position is.

488
00:44:55,610 --> 00:44:59,000
Looking old means that very soon you will become weak.

489
00:44:59,000 --> 00:45:04,640
To prevent deep wrinkles, you have to do this twice a day.

490
00:45:04,640 --> 00:45:08,770
I get it. You're working so hard.

491
00:45:08,780 --> 00:45:11,090
By the way, why did you come?

492
00:45:11,090 --> 00:45:13,180
After taking the etiquette class you ordered,

493
00:45:13,180 --> 00:45:17,960
I learned a lot of things about how a queen should behave.

494
00:45:17,960 --> 00:45:20,150
That pleases me.

495
00:45:21,260 --> 00:45:22,800
That's it. That's enough.

496
00:45:22,800 --> 00:45:24,750
Yes, Your Highness.

497
00:45:31,100 --> 00:45:33,230
But last night when we were sleeping together,

498
00:45:33,230 --> 00:45:38,110
I felt like I was lacking energy and didn't have any desire.

499
00:45:38,110 --> 00:45:41,530
I thought about the reason why and I realized,

500
00:45:43,110 --> 00:45:45,800
Since all the palace lakes have been drained,

501
00:45:45,800 --> 00:45:48,720
the yin energy is weak!
<i>(yin - female energy)</i>

502
00:45:48,720 --> 00:45:52,590
I feel like if the lakes are refilled with water, I will get pregnant with an heir right away.

503
00:45:52,590 --> 00:45:54,840
That cannot happen!

504
00:45:54,840 --> 00:45:58,080
<i>- Damn it!</i>
- You nearly lost your life in the lake!

505
00:45:58,080 --> 00:46:03,220
If we went by the book, it wouldn't be enough to put all your servants to death!

506
00:46:03,220 --> 00:46:08,980
We were only lenient since there was a joyous celebration of the royal wedding coming up and it wouldn't be good to shed blood!

507
00:46:09,630 --> 00:46:13,830
If you must refill the lakes, then let's do everything in order first.

508
00:46:13,830 --> 00:46:18,210
Hong Yeon and Lady Choi... and who else?

509
00:46:18,210 --> 00:46:21,940
I will severely punish everyone who's responsible!

510
00:46:21,940 --> 00:46:25,900
<i>Brutal... This old lady does not play around.</i>

511
00:46:25,900 --> 00:46:32,150
Three days to sleep together! In order to conceive an heir, I will get to it right away.

512
00:46:32,150 --> 00:46:34,270
In return, if you would refill the lake.

513
00:46:34,270 --> 00:46:36,130
Seven days!

514
00:46:36,130 --> 00:46:37,420
Five!

515
00:46:37,420 --> 00:46:40,310
You out there, take all those who serve Her Majesty and severely punish--

516
00:46:40,310 --> 00:46:42,120
Seven days!

517
00:46:42,120 --> 00:46:43,860
That's perfect.

518
00:46:43,860 --> 00:46:49,800
If you promise to refill the lake in seven days, I will conceive an heir.

519
00:46:51,770 --> 00:46:55,750
<i> An heir or whatever, once I leave, it's not my issue!</i>

520
00:47:15,140 --> 00:47:17,880
Eui Bin is here.

521
00:47:22,530 --> 00:47:27,610
My goodness, you are as elegant as I've heard.

522
00:47:27,610 --> 00:47:32,630
His Majesty has a very good eye for women.

523
00:47:32,630 --> 00:47:34,960
You're being too kind.

524
00:47:43,520 --> 00:47:45,240
It's a present.

525
00:47:45,250 --> 00:47:49,930
It's something very important for your palace life.

526
00:47:51,030 --> 00:47:53,120
Take it out and see.

527
00:48:07,770 --> 00:48:10,100
You know palace life is such that

528
00:48:10,100 --> 00:48:16,010
there's no one you can freely open your heart to; and once you feel uneasy, there's no end to it.

529
00:48:16,010 --> 00:48:20,670
Oh, right! What exactly is your birth date and hour?

530
00:48:20,670 --> 00:48:25,170
What would be best to do in order to conceive an heir?

531
00:48:26,480 --> 00:48:32,250
Oh my, listen to me! Physical compatibility with His Majesty would come first, right?

532
00:48:33,950 --> 00:48:39,800
By chance, if you need another strong talisman, let me know.

533
00:48:39,800 --> 00:48:44,040
I know a very skilled female Buddhist who specializes in curses.

534
00:48:44,040 --> 00:48:46,760
Last time, it worked out really well and--

535
00:48:46,760 --> 00:48:53,530
Your Highness, I apologize, but I only came here to assist His Majesty.

536
00:48:54,320 --> 00:48:58,010
I was... being foolish.

537
00:48:58,860 --> 00:49:03,230
My apologies, Your Highness. My words and actions were out of line.

538
00:49:03,230 --> 00:49:07,570
Not at all. Do not trouble yourself.

539
00:49:09,500 --> 00:49:13,030
Anyway, it seems that you will have to be alone

540
00:49:13,030 --> 00:49:15,880
for quite a while now that you were just installed.

541
00:49:15,880 --> 00:49:19,850
Too bad, I feel terrible for you.

542
00:49:19,850 --> 00:49:21,290
Pardon?

543
00:49:21,290 --> 00:49:26,360
The king and queen have seven days to conceive an heir.

544
00:49:26,360 --> 00:49:32,130
Usually, for a consummation day, thunder can't strike and there can't be fog nor wind.

545
00:49:32,130 --> 00:49:35,480
But this time the dates have been set day after day.

546
00:49:35,480 --> 00:49:37,850
Do not concern yourself.

547
00:49:37,860 --> 00:49:43,570
I doubt that His Majesty's feelings for you will change in the meantime.

548
00:50:11,430 --> 00:50:14,270
<i>You will surely...</i>

549
00:50:14,270 --> 00:50:17,450
<i>end up losing someone precious to you, too!</i>

550
00:50:37,990 --> 00:50:39,880
My Lady!

551
00:50:49,270 --> 00:50:52,830
I ruined it too much to fix in any way.

552
00:50:53,490 --> 00:50:56,680
It's too bad, but I'll have to throw it away.

553
00:50:56,680 --> 00:51:02,950
Oh, dear... Character-wise and in every way, you are best suited to be the queen.

554
00:51:02,950 --> 00:51:07,270
She's being so pushy with His Majesty while only trusting her connections.

555
00:51:07,270 --> 00:51:12,290
Bo-wol, the queen is like any other sovereign.

556
00:51:12,290 --> 00:51:16,060
There's a strict sense of duty pertaining to those above. Don't use harsh words.

557
00:51:16,060 --> 00:51:19,650
But still, she's using her ladies to fabricate the date that is best for conceiving.

558
00:51:19,650 --> 00:51:25,840
Also, you're being blamed for something you didn't even do! Why did that accident have to happen right when you were walking b—

559
00:51:31,510 --> 00:51:34,500
I'm not used to palace life yet.

560
00:51:34,500 --> 00:51:37,090
This mouth of mine.

561
00:51:37,090 --> 00:51:39,600
I apologize, My Lady.

562
00:51:42,190 --> 00:51:47,310
What can I do for His Majesty this time around?

563
00:51:59,360 --> 00:52:01,300
You told me to sleep at Eui Bin's quarters,

564
00:52:01,300 --> 00:52:04,400
but now you want to sleep with me, so you asked Her Royal Highness, the Grand Queen Dowager.

565
00:52:04,400 --> 00:52:08,160
It's really hard to read a woman's mind.

566
00:52:08,160 --> 00:52:10,010
I have a favor to ask you.

567
00:52:10,010 --> 00:52:11,710
Will you do it?

568
00:52:11,710 --> 00:52:15,440
Fine. Since it's a favor asked by My Queen.

569
00:52:15,440 --> 00:52:19,110
- Let's have a "no-touch" rule between us.
- I don't want to.

570
00:52:19,110 --> 00:52:21,990
- You said you would grant my wish.
- I've never heard of those words.

571
00:52:21,990 --> 00:52:23,900
You didn't know their meaning but rejected it unconditionally?

572
00:52:23,900 --> 00:52:27,130
Since I don't know their meaning, I don't want to do it.

573
00:52:29,230 --> 00:52:31,170
Listen carefully, Your Majesty.

574
00:52:31,170 --> 00:52:34,840
A "no-touch" rule means that let's live happily and delightfully, but separately.

575
00:52:34,840 --> 00:52:36,260
It has such a good meaning.

576
00:52:36,260 --> 00:52:40,160
So, for example, we said we would sleep together like this, but you would go to Eui Bin's quarters and be happy.

577
00:52:40,160 --> 00:52:42,240
Then I will be happy here, too.

578
00:52:42,240 --> 00:52:44,460
- So, let's do "no-touch."
- I see...

579
00:52:46,150 --> 00:52:47,880
But I don't want to.

580
00:52:47,880 --> 00:52:50,470
My god, why not?

581
00:52:50,470 --> 00:52:54,760
Somehow, your attitude is unpleasant.

582
00:52:54,760 --> 00:52:57,380
<i>What the... You total nut-job!</i>

583
00:52:59,310 --> 00:53:02,970
<i>Well, one nut-job knows very well how to handle another nut-job.</i>

584
00:53:05,150 --> 00:53:07,830
Then, since I don't remember well about last night,

585
00:53:07,830 --> 00:53:10,050
let's review it again.

586
00:53:10,050 --> 00:53:12,730
That TPN, okay?

587
00:53:13,470 --> 00:53:16,420
- TPN?
- That passionate night.

588
00:53:16,420 --> 00:53:21,880
Tonight is our true first night.

589
00:53:28,470 --> 00:53:30,340
If you say so...

590
00:53:39,340 --> 00:53:42,810
Hey! Hurry up, hurry! At this rate, we will get caught!

591
00:53:42,810 --> 00:53:46,480
A king never runs.

592
00:53:49,780 --> 00:53:51,500
Court Lady Choi!

593
00:54:00,730 --> 00:54:03,210
At this rate, you will really get in big trouble.

594
00:54:03,210 --> 00:54:07,800
I should see the hardships and worries of people for myself so that I can become a great queen.

595
00:54:07,800 --> 00:54:11,400
Your intention is noble, but this is too dangerous.

596
00:54:11,400 --> 00:54:14,050
If it was Your Majesty's order, I would do everything, even die at your order, but...

597
00:54:14,050 --> 00:54:15,530
The map.

598
00:54:18,880 --> 00:54:21,640
- But this time—
- The identity tag.

599
00:54:23,340 --> 00:54:24,900
I really can't let you do this.

600
00:54:24,900 --> 00:54:29,720
The name is... Lee Saeng Mang.
<i>(T/N: Modern Korean slang for "I'm doomed in this life.") </i>

601
00:54:29,720 --> 00:54:32,070
Why such an unfortunate name?

602
00:54:32,070 --> 00:54:33,760
Saeng means "take care" and Mang means "try hard."

603
00:54:33,760 --> 00:54:37,630
It's a good name, meaning take good care of the country and try hard for it.

604
00:54:38,280 --> 00:54:42,050
Well, all right, it's not my real name anyway.

605
00:54:42,050 --> 00:54:43,450
When is the curfew, you said?

606
00:54:43,450 --> 00:54:48,990
At the time of "Ja" (rat), the bell will toll 12 times and then the city's gate will be locked. <i>(Ja - 11:00 p.m. to 1:00 a.m.)</i>

607
00:54:48,990 --> 00:54:51,320
Ah, so you mean they will hit the bell.

608
00:54:51,320 --> 00:54:54,300
If you say the time of "Ja," that's 11:00 p.m.

609
00:54:56,640 --> 00:54:58,820
That's the prime time, though.

610
00:54:59,430 --> 00:55:03,500
Okay, I'll make sure to come back by then.

611
00:55:04,170 --> 00:55:06,580
No! By all means,

612
00:55:06,580 --> 00:55:09,640
I will stop you from going out, Your Majesty.

613
00:55:19,890 --> 00:55:24,460
Hong-yeon, what kind of person was I originally?

614
00:55:25,130 --> 00:55:27,880
Your Majesty was, well, always...

615
00:55:27,880 --> 00:55:32,080
You were benevolent and positive all the time,

616
00:55:32,080 --> 00:55:36,170
and you smiled a lot, and also you were very kind to other people.

617
00:55:37,100 --> 00:55:39,270
Don't you think it's better for me to hear from you,

618
00:55:39,270 --> 00:55:41,640
than from other people?

619
00:55:41,640 --> 00:55:43,410
I guess that's right.

620
00:55:44,520 --> 00:55:46,070
Then...

621
00:55:48,700 --> 00:55:52,000
<i>A while ago, one day you were reading a book.</i>

622
00:55:57,780 --> 00:56:01,480
<i>I can't read the book at all.</i>

623
00:56:01,480 --> 00:56:03,730
<i>How loudly your breathing sounds!</i>

624
00:56:03,730 --> 00:56:07,280
<i>Its noise rings in my ears so loudly.</i>

625
00:56:07,280 --> 00:56:10,820
<i>Look over there! Beat this man severely!</i>

626
00:56:10,820 --> 00:56:12,980
<i>I-I have rhinitis, that's why!</i>

627
00:56:12,980 --> 00:56:15,160
<i>Please forgive me, Your Highness!</i>

628
00:56:29,220 --> 00:56:32,610
<i>Your beat is one-fourth of a beat late.</i>

629
00:56:32,610 --> 00:56:35,050
<i>You have such a messy sense of the beat, </i>

630
00:56:35,050 --> 00:56:37,410
<i>so how dare you work as a teacher?</i>

631
00:56:38,320 --> 00:56:43,260
<i>Look over there! Beat this wench severely!</i>

632
00:56:43,260 --> 00:56:46,810
<i>Oh my goodness, that's so funny!</i>

633
00:56:48,160 --> 00:56:50,090
<i>Did you just laugh?</i>

634
00:56:50,090 --> 00:56:53,330
<i>I guess you girls have easy lives. </i>

635
00:56:53,330 --> 00:56:57,270
<i>Look over there! Beat these girls severely!</i>

636
00:56:57,270 --> 00:56:59,780
If one sighs, "How dare you sigh in front of me?"

637
00:56:59,780 --> 00:57:02,100
If one smells nice, "How dare you try to flirt?"

638
00:57:02,100 --> 00:57:05,470
If one walks with noise, "It's too noisy!" but if one walks gently, "Do you think you're the king?"

639
00:57:05,470 --> 00:57:10,330
Gosh! Since you nitpicked at every little detail of all the people in front of you and punished them harshly,

640
00:57:10,330 --> 00:57:14,190
your nickname is "The Witch of Royal Villa."

641
00:57:18,350 --> 00:57:20,070
I'm sorry.

642
00:57:20,880 --> 00:57:24,710
I was just trying to relay the stories vividly but got carried away.

643
00:57:24,710 --> 00:57:28,460
<i>So, not just one or two people would want to push this woman into the lake.</i>

644
00:57:28,460 --> 00:57:31,210
That's why those palace maids earlier...

645
00:57:31,210 --> 00:57:34,800
That's because all of them don't know your true self.

646
00:57:34,800 --> 00:57:36,410
Then, do you know it?

647
00:57:36,410 --> 00:57:37,780
Of course, I do.

648
00:57:37,780 --> 00:57:41,180
The Your Majesty, whom I've been serving since my childhood,

649
00:57:41,180 --> 00:57:43,600
is originally warm.

650
00:57:43,600 --> 00:57:47,720
And how smart you are! Once you make up your mind on something, you surely make it happen, no matter what.

651
00:57:47,720 --> 00:57:49,830
You're such an awesome person.

652
00:57:51,260 --> 00:57:55,480
It's just because you were a little lonely in this palace,

653
00:57:55,480 --> 00:58:00,380
since His Majesty the King openly shows his affection to another woman...

654
00:58:01,970 --> 00:58:05,160
But I see this woman isn't always lonely,

655
00:58:05,160 --> 00:58:08,020
as she has a person who understands her like this.

656
00:58:08,020 --> 00:58:09,760
"This... woman"?

657
00:58:09,760 --> 00:58:13,690
I mean, I'm not lonely, thanks to you.

658
00:58:15,050 --> 00:58:17,110
Oh, please, Your Majesty.

659
00:58:19,320 --> 00:58:22,490
Hong-yeon, don't worry and have a good night's sleep.

660
00:58:22,490 --> 00:58:26,540
For you, at least, I will never get caught.

661
00:58:28,210 --> 00:58:30,610
I'm going to kill you all!

662
00:58:30,610 --> 00:58:32,990
Just gouge out this eye as well!

663
00:58:32,990 --> 00:58:37,370
I can't watch my wife and child become slaves, too!

664
00:58:37,370 --> 00:58:40,130
If you don't have money for tax, it's only right to pay it with your body.

665
00:58:40,130 --> 00:58:41,760
T-That sinful bastard!

666
00:58:41,760 --> 00:58:43,670
If I'm a sinner,

667
00:58:43,670 --> 00:58:45,580
my sin is to have brought a child

668
00:58:45,580 --> 00:58:48,650
into this damnable world!

669
00:58:52,020 --> 00:58:54,220
Don't come near! Don't!

670
00:58:54,220 --> 00:58:56,870
That crazy bastard is trying to add treason to his crimes!

671
00:58:56,870 --> 00:59:00,190
If killing such bastards like you is treason, I'll commit treason.

672
00:59:00,190 --> 00:59:02,270
Sure, I'll do it!

673
00:59:02,270 --> 00:59:04,300
Dam-hyang's father!

674
00:59:06,150 --> 00:59:07,910
Don't.

675
00:59:08,970 --> 00:59:11,660
Even so...

676
00:59:12,500 --> 00:59:16,160
But those bastards are killing us every day!

677
00:59:16,160 --> 00:59:18,980
What do you mean, don't!

678
00:59:20,640 --> 00:59:22,580
Dam-hyang...

679
00:59:29,920 --> 00:59:31,510
<i>- Catch him!</i>
- Get out of my way!

680
01:00:04,970 --> 01:00:07,520
Father, you've arrived.

681
01:00:07,520 --> 01:00:10,810
Yes. How were your travels?

682
01:00:10,810 --> 01:00:14,740
I'm sorry that I was absent when there were important events in our household.

683
01:00:14,740 --> 01:00:19,520
Have you made up your mind? Do you know what position you'd like?

684
01:00:19,520 --> 01:00:25,390
I've decided the direction of my dream but I haven't decided the magnitude of my dream.

685
01:00:25,390 --> 01:00:27,680
The magnitude?

686
01:00:29,740 --> 01:00:34,560
Sure. I will trust you and not rush you.

687
01:00:34,560 --> 01:00:39,000
The truth is, while you were gone, something did happen.

688
01:00:39,000 --> 01:00:43,940
Her Majesty the Queen fell into a lake the night before the wedding.

689
01:00:43,940 --> 01:00:49,790
After falling into the lake, she lost consciousness for a day and the wedding was postponed.

690
01:00:49,790 --> 01:00:54,570
How is she now? Is she all right?

691
01:01:04,650 --> 01:01:06,400
Wait!

692
01:01:11,690 --> 01:01:18,170
Seeing that a man, whom I've never seen before in the palace, is looking around in a rush...

693
01:01:18,170 --> 01:01:22,680
It's your first time in the palace and you've lost your way, haven't you?

694
01:01:22,680 --> 01:01:24,510
I was the same my first time, too.

695
01:01:24,510 --> 01:01:26,570
You're right!

696
01:01:31,890 --> 01:01:35,410
But why do you look so familiar?

697
01:01:38,530 --> 01:01:44,110
<i>Seeing his luxurious outfit and his confident attitude with no wariness of other people... </i>

698
01:01:44,900 --> 01:01:47,210
<i>definitely a silver spoon.</i>

699
01:01:47,210 --> 01:01:49,210
That's what I was going to say.

700
01:01:49,210 --> 01:01:53,170
Aren't you that famous young master? You're not only from a prestigious family but also very handsome.

701
01:01:53,170 --> 01:01:56,830
Rumor says you're excellent in both literary and martial arts. Your name was...

702
01:01:56,830 --> 01:02:01,410
Kim Hwan. I'm Hwan from the Andong Kim family.

703
01:02:01,410 --> 01:02:02,380
<i>Gosh, he's a relative.</i>

704
01:02:02,380 --> 01:02:05,270
Am I that famous?

705
01:02:05,270 --> 01:02:06,880
Of course, you are.

706
01:02:06,880 --> 01:02:12,190
Well, the rumor spread all over the place. Well, it's my honor to be acquainted.

707
01:02:12,190 --> 01:02:16,590
I'm also on my way to get out of the palace, so let's go together.

708
01:02:16,590 --> 01:02:18,690
Ah, that's the way I came from, though.

709
01:02:18,690 --> 01:02:21,280
Oh, I was mistaken for a moment in this darkness.

710
01:02:27,270 --> 01:02:29,980
- Bam! Beheaded.
<i> - Wow...</i>

711
01:02:29,980 --> 01:02:32,750
<i> He's so freaking talkative. How can he keep talking without any break? </i>

712
01:02:32,750 --> 01:02:36,090
...the energy of this place is a bit damp.

713
01:02:36,090 --> 01:02:41,760
That's why His Majesty the King also has a nightmare every night.

714
01:02:41,760 --> 01:02:44,230
A nightmare?

715
01:02:44,230 --> 01:02:49,720
