719
01:03:03,230 --> 01:03:06,280
No, don't worry as there are many people coming and going.

720
01:03:08,400 --> 01:03:10,940
<i>[Lee Saeng Mang]</i>

721
01:03:17,440 --> 01:03:22,040
Ah, to commemorate becoming good friends with you, I'm thinking of going to the gisaeng house. <i>(gisaeng - courtesan)</i>

722
01:03:22,040 --> 01:03:24,260
Which one is the best in this city?

723
01:03:24,260 --> 01:03:27,930
Oktajeong! That's the best place.

724
01:03:27,930 --> 01:03:30,430
It's the women's laughing sounds, "Ho, ho, ho!"

725
01:03:30,430 --> 01:03:34,760
Like the sound from hitting jade, that's why it's called Oktajeong. <i>(Ok - jade and Ta - hit)</i>

726
01:03:35,910 --> 01:03:39,200
Let's go together. Seeing the moon shining so brightly tonight,

727
01:03:39,200 --> 01:03:42,720
this is the perfect night to enjoy a taste of the arts!

728
01:03:44,350 --> 01:03:45,650
Here it is.

729
01:03:45,650 --> 01:03:47,280
Let's go.

730
01:03:47,280 --> 01:03:48,500
You're working hard.

731
01:03:48,500 --> 01:03:50,190
Ah, yes.

732
01:03:51,050 --> 01:03:53,180
You seem to be at the same age as me

733
01:03:53,180 --> 01:03:57,810
and even have the same hobby. How nice to be acquainted with you.

734
01:03:57,810 --> 01:04:03,150
Oh, by the way, I haven't heard your name yet. Your name is...

735
01:04:03,150 --> 01:04:05,560
My name is Lee Saeng Mang.

736
01:04:09,880 --> 01:04:14,300
Lee Saeng Mang, meaning "I'm doomed in this life."

737
01:04:17,910 --> 01:04:19,620
Good work.

738
01:04:24,800 --> 01:04:27,090
<i>What's your name?</i>

739
01:04:36,970 --> 01:04:38,520
I'm sorry.

740
01:04:38,520 --> 01:04:41,110
<i>Open your mouth!</i>

741
01:04:47,550 --> 01:04:50,160
Here we have a female guest.

742
01:04:50,160 --> 01:04:52,270
What do you mean, to a perfectly fine young man?

743
01:04:52,270 --> 01:04:56,830
We don't accept female guests.

744
01:05:02,880 --> 01:05:07,350
Girls! We have a young master!

745
01:05:27,660 --> 01:05:29,790
Yeah!

746
01:05:34,620 --> 01:05:38,020
It's my great honor to meet you, sir.

747
01:05:45,310 --> 01:05:48,420
Please allow me to offer a drink—

748
01:05:52,870 --> 01:05:56,030
I don't drink more than three glasses of alcohol per day.

749
01:05:56,030 --> 01:06:01,400
Since I've already had the second one, I'd like to have the third one with my friend.

750
01:06:02,890 --> 01:06:05,820
Since he's very upright, you know.

751
01:06:07,120 --> 01:06:11,820
It's Sir Yu's son who passed the Grand State Examination this time.

752
01:06:11,820 --> 01:06:13,760
Congratulations.

753
01:06:13,760 --> 01:06:19,570
Well, despite his skills, he couldn't get a good position in Hanyang. <i>(Hanyang - what is now Seoul)</i>

754
01:06:19,570 --> 01:06:25,200
As long as you're leading him in the right direction, I'll show you my gratitude, no matter how much it is.

755
01:06:26,550 --> 01:06:32,880
Are you telling me now to sell a government official post for money?

756
01:06:32,880 --> 01:06:37,370
Well, what I meant was... because I think I would be very grateful.

757
01:06:37,370 --> 01:06:41,790
By the way, as far as I know, it has been a while since your son passed the test,

758
01:06:41,790 --> 01:06:42,980
why now?

759
01:06:42,980 --> 01:06:44,970
That was...

760
01:06:47,430 --> 01:06:50,770
You must have contacted the Pungyang Jo family first.

761
01:06:52,250 --> 01:06:56,800
As my wife's family is a distant relative to the Pungyang Jo family,

762
01:06:56,800 --> 01:06:59,430
I'm deeply ashamed.

763
01:07:10,230 --> 01:07:12,620
I fully understand your desperation,

764
01:07:12,620 --> 01:07:18,210
worrying if your talented son might not be able to spread his wings due to his family's lack of virtue.

765
01:07:18,210 --> 01:07:22,840
I'll give you my support to let him clear his name and get a position in the Royal Secretary's office.

766
01:07:22,840 --> 01:07:24,760
In the Royal Secretary's office?

767
01:07:24,760 --> 01:07:28,190
Thank you! Thank you, thank you!

768
01:07:28,190 --> 01:07:30,240
Forget about the gratitude.

769
01:07:30,240 --> 01:07:34,930
Instead, I need a friend.

770
01:07:34,930 --> 01:07:37,690
A friend who can give up his life for me.

771
01:07:38,980 --> 01:07:41,210
All the lives of my family

772
01:07:41,210 --> 01:07:45,360
are yours from now on, Sir!

773
01:07:49,610 --> 01:07:51,650
Please pour me a glass,

774
01:07:51,650 --> 01:07:53,490
as we have become friends now.

775
01:07:53,490 --> 01:07:57,500
Yes, Sir, much obliged!

776
01:08:06,250 --> 01:08:09,420
- Come in, girls!
<i>- Yes, Sir.</i>

777
01:08:10,610 --> 01:08:16,410
Now let's enjoy tonight like beasts until we get totally drunk!

778
01:08:18,690 --> 01:08:20,930
Oh, come on!

779
01:08:20,930 --> 01:08:23,000
You're so funny!

780
01:08:23,000 --> 01:08:24,070
Please come here.

781
01:08:24,070 --> 01:08:27,390
Young Master, please accept a glass.

782
01:08:29,010 --> 01:08:31,140
Young Master!

783
01:08:32,520 --> 01:08:34,770
You're so elegant.

784
01:08:35,590 --> 01:08:40,760
Who will untie my string tonight?

785
01:08:50,970 --> 01:08:54,310
In the 20 years of my gisaeng career,

786
01:08:54,310 --> 01:08:57,530
I've never seen such a perverted man like him.

787
01:09:18,850 --> 01:09:21,730
This is miserable.

788
01:09:23,570 --> 01:09:27,870
Even at a place like this, we should drink by ourselves...

789
01:09:27,870 --> 01:09:30,530
This isn't the time to say such things.

790
01:09:30,530 --> 01:09:33,640
The item wasn't in the secret storage room, which we thought was the most highly probable place.

791
01:09:33,640 --> 01:09:36,970
Then, there is one last place left, the house of the king's father-in-law.

792
01:09:36,970 --> 01:09:41,060
But of all people, they want to appoint the king's father-in-law as the Commander of the Royal Guard,

793
01:09:41,060 --> 01:09:43,080
so it will be even harder to sneak in.

794
01:09:43,080 --> 01:09:47,570
When they say they want to take over the Royal Guard, it means they want to control the king's life.

795
01:09:47,570 --> 01:09:51,320
It will also take just a moment for them to catch the king's bodyguards who are disguised as regular royal guards.

796
01:09:51,320 --> 01:09:55,020
What? Then, we'd really be in a dire situation.

797
01:09:55,020 --> 01:10:00,210
If those bodyguards get their identities exposed and get dismissed, the job of following after corrupt people every night

798
01:10:00,210 --> 01:10:02,400
and the job of finding the illegal ledger and attack their storages,

799
01:10:02,400 --> 01:10:04,620
all of that must be done by me and you, Prince Yeongpyeong.

800
01:10:04,620 --> 01:10:06,900
We work as royal guards during the day and as assassins at night.

801
01:10:06,900 --> 01:10:10,580
We will suffer from a too heavy workload, you know?

802
01:10:13,090 --> 01:10:17,610
Did you call me all the way from Ganghwa Island to boss me around like this?

803
01:10:19,930 --> 01:10:21,590
When I was on my way to Hanyang,

804
01:10:21,590 --> 01:10:26,300
I had a great dream in this heart of young blood.

805
01:10:26,300 --> 01:10:30,550
"I will become successful by selling my friend's name!"

806
01:10:31,840 --> 01:10:34,980
You're the one who followed me frantically

807
01:10:34,980 --> 01:10:38,430
on my words that I would save this rotting Joseon.

808
01:10:38,430 --> 01:10:40,600
You didn't say it like that.

809
01:10:40,600 --> 01:10:46,710
Since you kept talking about Hanyang, I asked you and this is how you answered exactly.

810
01:10:50,220 --> 01:10:52,970
<i>What on earth are you going to Hanyang for?</i>

811
01:10:55,830 --> 01:11:01,000
<i>I'm going to give this rotting and dying Joseon ddongchim! (meaning 'shove it up one's ass)</i>

812
01:11:06,900 --> 01:11:08,620
Yes, I said that.

813
01:11:09,600 --> 01:11:13,940
I didn't know that such stirring words meant I should work my ass off like this.

814
01:11:13,940 --> 01:11:19,150
How foolish this me in the past was.

815
01:11:19,150 --> 01:11:22,270
- Now is greatly different from the past, isn't it?
- Eh?

816
01:11:27,290 --> 01:11:32,010
By any chance, did they notice our moves and now are trying to control the Royal Guard?

817
01:11:32,010 --> 01:11:37,300
No way. If they noticed, they would've put some spies in here to listen to our words even now.

818
01:11:37,300 --> 01:11:39,190
They might...

819
01:11:41,880 --> 01:11:44,110
<i>Great!</i>

820
01:11:44,110 --> 01:11:47,120
<i>Damn it.</i>

821
01:11:47,120 --> 01:11:49,410
So tight.

822
01:11:51,350 --> 01:11:53,380
<i>Oh, I'm getting drunk!</i>

823
01:11:57,530 --> 01:12:00,180
Where the heck is the restroom?

824
01:12:03,920 --> 01:12:06,390
There it is!

825
01:12:38,110 --> 01:12:39,990
You know...

826
01:12:41,580 --> 01:12:43,650
I'm so jealous of you.

827
01:12:43,650 --> 01:12:46,480
I used to have one of those.

828
01:12:46,480 --> 01:12:49,070
That thing which is

829
01:12:49,070 --> 01:12:53,110
no longer mine... Bye!

830
01:12:53,110 --> 01:12:58,380
My dragon! Bye-bye, my yong-yong <i>(dragon)</i>!

831
01:13:01,310 --> 01:13:04,420
I can't even pee while standing.

832
01:13:05,270 --> 01:13:09,400
This dirty world where only the haves can pee while standing.

833
01:13:09,400 --> 01:13:12,830
It's so sad that even my pee stopped

834
01:13:12,830 --> 01:13:15,800
and my tears stopped, too.

835
01:13:29,610 --> 01:13:32,460
Now that I don't have my dragon,

836
01:13:32,460 --> 01:13:35,660
I don't have my balls either.

837
01:13:35,660 --> 01:13:38,790
If it's going to be this way, they should've killed me.

838
01:13:38,790 --> 01:13:41,680
What is this cruelty you've done? Eh?!

839
01:13:44,290 --> 01:13:46,480
<i>Here, accept mine. </i>

840
01:13:57,000 --> 01:13:59,440
Huh...

841
01:13:59,440 --> 01:14:03,700
Maybe they also caught our fabrication of light red made with pig's blood.

842
01:14:03,700 --> 01:14:06,300
To put the king's father-in-law in the position of Commander of the Royal Guard

843
01:14:06,300 --> 01:14:09,850
is actually proof that they haven't figured out our moves.

844
01:14:09,850 --> 01:14:12,370
If they had found it out, they would've

845
01:14:12,370 --> 01:14:15,900
already beheaded you two, my brother and Officer Hong.

846
01:14:17,960 --> 01:14:19,480
Then, why all of a sudden...

847
01:14:19,480 --> 01:14:24,350
Nothing has changed except for the queen and Lady Eui Bin entering the palace,

848
01:14:24,350 --> 01:14:27,760
so maybe the queen used her influence to keep Lady Eui Bin in check.

849
01:14:28,710 --> 01:14:33,630
As soon as the royal wedding is done, she's putting a sword to her husband's neck.

850
01:14:33,630 --> 01:14:36,040
How scary this woman is.

851
01:14:36,040 --> 01:14:40,000
As the situation isn't in our favor, let's put a stop to the plan to find that item.

852
01:14:40,000 --> 01:14:43,510
What we're preparing is the fight for power and justification.

853
01:14:43,510 --> 01:14:46,930
The only way to punish those powerful people

854
01:14:46,930 --> 01:14:52,360
<i>is to prove their corruption with concrete documental evidence. </i>

855
01:14:52,360 --> 01:14:55,800
Securing that key evidence, their double accounting book,

856
01:14:55,800 --> 01:14:57,280
cannot be delayed.

857
01:14:57,280 --> 01:14:59,480
Then, what shall we do?

858
01:14:59,480 --> 01:15:03,360
Let's obediently give away the position of the Commander of the Royal Guard.

859
01:15:03,360 --> 01:15:06,180
- But—
- If we throw them a prey, they will be too busy eating it

860
01:15:06,180 --> 01:15:08,360
to look around at their surroundings.

861
01:15:08,360 --> 01:15:10,830
If their attention is focused on the commander's appointment,

862
01:15:10,830 --> 01:15:14,470
that will help us find the location of their double accounting book.

863
01:15:14,470 --> 01:15:18,910
We can take that commander position back while they think they have it.

864
01:15:18,910 --> 01:15:21,200
It's hard not to lose the position,

865
01:15:21,200 --> 01:15:22,690
but it's even harder to take it back.

866
01:15:22,690 --> 01:15:25,190
The Commander of the Royal Guard is the position of a warrior.

867
01:15:25,190 --> 01:15:27,210
Even if he's appointed, it's in name only.

868
01:15:27,210 --> 01:15:31,160
If he can't physically work in the position, he can't stay there.

869
01:15:31,890 --> 01:15:36,860
On the first day of his appointment, let's make a small accident to drag him out of it.

870
01:15:36,860 --> 01:15:40,000
What if Kim Mun-geun is quicker at sensing things than we anticipated,

871
01:15:40,000 --> 01:15:43,170
and figures out the existence of our bodyguards right away?

872
01:15:43,170 --> 01:15:45,950
Then, we will have to use our last resort

873
01:15:45,950 --> 01:15:49,980
to secure the Royal Guard as well as get their double accounting book.

874
01:15:49,980 --> 01:15:52,410
If you have such a good method, why don't we use it now?

875
01:15:52,410 --> 01:15:55,360
What is this last resort?

876
01:15:57,800 --> 01:15:59,500
Assassination.

877
01:16:04,460 --> 01:16:07,360
He will end up that way anyway.

878
01:16:24,430 --> 01:16:27,610
<i>What's this gloomy room? </i>

879
01:16:46,820 --> 01:16:50,890
Damn it, the bell is tolling!

880
01:17:00,470 --> 01:17:01,880
Wasn't that the queen?

881
01:17:01,880 --> 01:17:04,040
Did she even disguise herself as a man and follow us?

882
01:17:04,040 --> 01:17:05,700
We can't let her go like this.

883
01:17:05,700 --> 01:17:08,690
However, we don't even know how much she heard

884
01:17:08,690 --> 01:17:10,330
and I'm sure she's not here alone.

885
01:17:10,330 --> 01:17:14,160
That's why we must hurry up, chase after her, and silence her.

886
01:17:20,690 --> 01:17:22,560
Your Majesty.

887
01:17:30,690 --> 01:17:34,010
This isn't the time you can hesitate out of personal feelings.

888
01:17:36,220 --> 01:17:38,990
I'll do it myself.

889
01:18:19,980 --> 01:18:21,790
Ten times...

890
01:18:24,420 --> 01:18:26,920
Eleven times, okay...

891
01:18:28,690 --> 01:18:30,960
If it rings one more time, I'm done for.

